text: @SpeakerPelosi Too little too late, Why did @SpeakerPelosi wait to deal with the #coronavirus. Nancy Pelosi needs to apologize for her lack a action until now. @SpeakerPelosi did not need to wait until after people died, so she could try to impeach @realDonaldTrump  again. She crossed the line.
